I checked the latest codebase and didn't find the test cases you mentioned.
testLargeRegionsWithEviction() in CacheDataRegionConfigurationTest(master branch).

@liyuj Just add suggested test to this test class in your pull request. Run test and make sure the issue was fixed. Seems, we need explicit cast in a subsequent lines after memory allocate:
`GridUnsafe.setMemory(..., int -> long, ...)`

Thanks for your review, all your suggestions have been fixed.
